MOTIONS and OPERATIONS in VISUAL MODE
-------------------------------------

    Enter v to enter VISUAL mode or V to enter VISUAL LINE mode. Delete,
    yank, and change work as you'd expect.

    v{motion}{operation}
    vjjjjjd

